RawQuestion: what is the largest nation in europe?
ProcessedQuestion: what is the largest nation in europe

Parses.Sparql:
PREFIX ns: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?x
WHERE {
FILTER (?x != ns:m.02j9z)
FILTER (!isLiteral(?x) OR lang(?x) = '' OR langMatches(lang(?x), 'en'))
ns:m.02j9z ns:base.locations.continents.countries_within ?x .
?x ns:topic_server.population_number ?sk0 .
}
ORDER BY DESC(xsd:float(?sk0))
LIMIT 1
